text: Phryneta luctuosa is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Murray in 1870. It is known from Cameroon and Nigeria.BioLib.cz - Phryneta luctuosa. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1870
title: Phryneta luctuosa
